creator: Arthur Pink
description:
LibriVox recording of The Sovereignty of God by Arthur Pink.
Read in English by Greg Giordano; graemegrant; Kimberly Dion; Anna Roberts; gloriousjob; J L Raimundo; KHand
In the following pages an attempt has been made to examine anew in the light of God's Word some of the profoundest questions which can engage the human mind. (Summary by Arthur Pink)
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

M4B Format Available
